Stellar Network Configuration

Options: https://horizon-testnet.stellar.org or https://horizon.stellar.org

STELLAR_HORIZON_URL=https://horizon-testnet.stellar.org
STELLAR_NETWORK_PASSPHRASE="Test SDF Network ; September 2015"

Soroban RPC (for Smart Contracts)

Default for Testnet: https://soroban-testnet.stellar.org

SOROBAN_RPC_URL=https://soroban-testnet.stellar.org

Aether Bridge Identity (DO NOT use real keys here)

The Public Key for the Bridge Account

BRIDGE_PUBLIC_KEY=G.......................................................

The Secret Key (Only for local testing, use a placeholder)

BRIDGE_SECRET_KEY=S.......................................................

Asset Configuration

ASSET_CODE=USDC
ISSUER_ADDRESS=G.......................................................

Gateway Port

PORT=3000
LOG_LEVEL=info
